# FAST + DATA-COMPLETE + FINAL SAVED TO GOOGLE DRIVE
#
# Main design:
#   1) Read original data from Google Drive.
#   2) Process and cache intermediate city-level files locally in /content for speed.
#   3) Save final NPZ/CSV reports to local first.
#   4) Copy final outputs to Google Drive at the end.
#   5) Optionally sync city caches to Google Drive every N cities.
#
# This version preserves:
#   X, y, channels
#   sample_city_id, sample_city_name
#   sample_year, sample_month, sample_yyyymm
#   sample_row, sample_col
#   sample_lon, sample_lat
#   sample_era_row, sample_era_col
#   sample_spatial_block_id
#   sample_city_year, sample_city_year_month
#
# Important:
#   City ID is saved as metadata but is NOT used as model predictor by default.
# ============================================================

